The paper proposes a new neural network activation function and evaluates its performance on various computer vision, natural language processing, and speech tasks. This suggests that the paper could belong to several arXiv CS sub-categories, including cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) which focuses on neural networks and their applications, cs.LG (Machine Learning) which covers a broad range of machine learning topics, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) which deals with image and video analysis, cs.CL (Computation and Language) which covers natural language processing, and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) which encompasses a wide range of AI-related topics.
